title: A Devil's Chronicle - Corin Hamilton
description:
An excellent e-book from Corin Hamilton about a man that achieves immortality through technology and uses it to make the world a better place -- until it all goes to shit and he has to go back in time to undo his legacy.  

If the road to Hell is paved with good intentions, then the path back to Absolution is beat with truly dark deeds.

As always, if you like the book, pay for it.  Support the authors that work so hard to entertain you.  If nothing else, give them an honest review.
